headline: EastGroup Properties (EGP) Q1 FFO and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: EastGroup Properties (EGP) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 0.47% and 2.44%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
